author_ssm: Yookyung Kwon (March-July 2003), Leif Sorensen (July-September 2004), Melanie Meyers-Cushman (December 2004)
abstract_ssm: Writer and visual artist Michele Zackheim is the author of two novels: Violette's Embrace and Einstein's Daughter: the Search for Lieserl. The Michele Zackheim Papers comprise research materials for the novels, including correspondence, manuscripts, legal documents, publicity material, photographs, books such as biographies and tourist guides, and audio and video cassettes.
